Package owl.ltl

Class EquivalenceClass

  • java.lang.Object
    • owl.ltl.EquivalenceClass
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    LtlLanguageExpressible
    public class EquivalenceClass
extends Object
implements LtlLanguageExpressible
    EquivalenceClass interface. The general contract of this interface is: If two implementing objects were created from different factories, implies and equals have to return false.
